ActNorthern Pipeline Act
SubjectAgreement with Foothills Pipe Lines (South Yukon) Ltd.
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Natural Resources Canada to amend the EASEMENT AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and FOOTHILLS PIPE LINES (South Yukon) Ltd. in order to provide additional time to begin construction of Stage Two (the northern section) of the Alaska Highway Gas Pipeline.
